{"tid":211550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（死神來了）8歲童玩機動遊戲，意外慘死","createTime":"2017-04-21T16:48:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T23:59:23.000Z","uid":29314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b1e71fd5e34735a992448b3b2adb1c837cd64bc7","tid":211550,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T16:48:21.000Z","msg":"[quote]<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170420/photo/bkncn-20170420170018918-0420_05011_001_01p.jpg?20170420195235\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170420%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170420170018918-0420_05011_001_01p.jpg%3F20170420195235&h=347c65a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\n\r<br />\n昨日上午，博羅縣實驗小學安排一至三年級的學生，前往東莞市水濂山樂民遊藝園參加社會實踐活動。豈料就讀二年級的劉姓學生在排隊等候玩「歡樂旅行車」項目時，不慎摔落運轉中的軌道內，當場被輾斃。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170420/photo/bkncn-20170420170018918-0420_05011_001_02b.jpg?20170420195235\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170420%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170420170018918-0420_05011_001_02b.jpg%3F20170420195235&h=80869924&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n死者父親接獲消息後趕抵現場，並翻看事發時的閉路電視畫面。劉父稱當時機動車正在運行，而兒子則排在龍頭，非常靠近軌道，由於人多，兒子不慎摔倒並立即被捲入軌道裏。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n劉父表示，事發後，其他正排隊的學生都被眼前的一幕嚇倒，恐慌聲不斷響起，大家都顯得驚慌失措，且急速後退。他哽咽地說：「場面慘烈，一個活生生的生命這樣遭輾壓死亡。恐慌的場面一直浮現在我腦海。」<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170420/photo/bkncn-20170420170018918-0420_05011_001_03b.jpg?20170420195235\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170420%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170420170018918-0420_05011_001_03b.jpg%3F20170420195235&h=01a3fc03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170420/photo/bkncn-20170420170018918-0420_05011_001_04b.jpg?20170420195235\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170420%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170420170018918-0420_05011_001_04b.jpg%3F20170420195235&h=30bbcb74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n據博羅縣委宣傳部官方微博今日通報，事發後帶隊老師已立即報警求助，並疏散其他學生，目前其餘學生已全部返抵博羅縣並由家長接走。通報又指，當局將為受影響學生進行心理輔導，並協調東莞市有關部門依法處理事故。而東莞市有關部門已成立事故調查處理小組，徹查事故原因。"},{"pid":"cb1459c3018f9b3cfd6c05ccdb393c992256672b","tid":211550,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T17:18:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"029ff9a5f126e0005a361677746154700565c9ba","tid":211550,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T23:25:01.000Z","msg":"支那無一個是無古架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58d2a3115373cf676a2f8afeef64cf0be6bb3ae7","tid":211550,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T23:38:40.000Z","msg":"其實點解仲有人夠薑玩支那既機動遊戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e35539b9301ced0ec1e61b37be3f43ea98bd35c","tid":211550,"uid":50801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T23:39:12.000Z","msg":"排隊點會排到仆街死嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪條細路一路排一路同人玩推手輸左跟著向後仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08ef711e7aef5ea650b1d7d68facb90cb9dbd426","tid":211550,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T23:42:28.000Z","msg":"因為大部分支那人都是在純養中，根本就不清楚自由的情況！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好似五毛都一樣，明明自己是最大的受害人，但一樣都要為主子發聲！"},{"pid":"bbaa0d88c682d0e104929409421c0c06ea7939a5","tid":211550,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T23:51:17.000Z","msg":"癡線嫁咁都可以出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33c7b5a0a1bc6895f7afc9849f4710a832609884","tid":211550,"uid":2752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T23:53:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>排隊點會排到仆街死嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪條細路一路排一路同人玩推手輸左跟著向後仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係未中國式排隊，跟手有人後面頂前未仆街死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13c824706814646f4896bad644a2f3ef43858201","tid":211550,"uid":41821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T23:58:38.000Z","msg":"係咪過度活躍症？"},{"pid":"2591054fa49bb6e005eab7d69e099a0bcef8aab6","tid":211550,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T23:59:23.000Z","msg":"積下口德啦"}]}